        "timestamp": "2017-08-31 17:01:47.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIs this still necessary if people already have these repos defined in their ~/.m2/settings.xml locally?\nAlso, let's keep ecomp-staging off the list.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "7367f222d2c7934c39ee7b569d716d49e259f455",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 11,
