          "username": "nabero"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-04 08:14:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nI removed ecomp-staging. \n\nUnfortunately if we don't add this, no project inheriting from oparent is compilable out of the box. \n\nI would rather add some default configuration (ppl can still override them using their settings.xml) and be able to compile a project by simply use usual commands than having something that needs a specific configuration before being able to test it.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
